<html><head></head><body><h2>Poch to miss Southampton and Liverpool games after receiving 2 match ban</h2><p>Mauricio Pochettino will miss two matches after receiving his punishment from the FA for the incident involving Mike Dean after Tottenham's defeat at Burnley.</p><p>The Spurs boss hinted at the prospect after the win in Borussia Dortmund and now it has been confirmed.</p> <p>"Mauricio Pochettino has been fined £10,000 and will serve a two-match touchline ban following an Independent Regulatory Commission hearing," read an FA statement.</p> <p>"The Tottenham Hotspur manager accepted an improper conduct charge from The FA, which resulted from his language and/or behaviour – both on the pitch and in or around the tunnel area – at the end of the game against Burnley on 23 February."</p> <p>Pochettino will now miss the matches at Southampton and Liverpool this month and he had said after the Champions League win that he was very unhappy with what he knew was coming from the FA.</p> <figure class="in-article-image" data-mod="image" itemprop="image" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/ImageObject"> <meta itemprop="url" content="https://i2-prod.football.london/incoming/article15913462.ece/ALTERNATES/s615b/0_GettyImages-1133182173.jpg"> <meta itemprop="width" content="615"> <meta itemprop="height" content="410"> <div class="outer"> <div class="mod-image"> <img data-src="https://i2-prod.football.london/incoming/article15913462.ece/ALTERNATES/s615b/0_GettyImages-1133182173.jpg" alt="" content="https://i2-prod.football.london/incoming/article15913462.ece/ALTERNATES/s615b/0_GettyImages-1133182173.jpg"> </div> </div> <figcaption> <span class="caption" itemprop="description">Mauricio Pochettino</span> </figcaption> </figure> <p>"I am not going to talk because it easy to pay with me and you are going to see tomorrow why I am not going to talk," replied Pochettino.&nbsp;</p> <p>"I am very disappointed, I don't think that is going to change but I don't care, we are going to be strong.&nbsp;</p> <p>"If we are not going to receive a help from our football people in our country only I can laugh. You are going to see tomorrow why I am not so happy with the people."</p> <aside class="read-more-links">  </aside>   <p>  </p><p></p></body></html>